Weighted edge list from Wikipedia example

Source: R/wiki_graph.R
wiki_graph.Rd

A small weighted directed graph used in Dijkstra examples.

Usage

data(wiki_graph)

Format

A data frame with three columns:

v1

From node (numeric)

v2

To node (numeric)

w

Edge weight (non-negative numeric)

References

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dijkstra's_algorithm

Examples

data(wiki_graph)
head(wiki_graph)
#>   v1 v2  w
#> 1  1  2  7
#> 2  1  3  9
#> 3  1  6 14
#> 4  2  1  7
#> 5  2  3 10
#> 6  2  4 15
